  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Replaced "Verified" with "Responsible" in the page titles and meta descriptions of all nine species pages under <a href="/find-breeders" class="text-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] hover:underline">/find-breeders</a> (dogs, cats, horses, goats, rabbits, sheep, cattle, alpacas, llamas). "Verified" in marketing copy conflicts with the 3-layer trust posture, which prohibits verify/vet/vouch claims. The rabbits description also swapped "verified operations" for "active operations". Titles now read "Find Responsible [Species] Breeders | BreederHQ". Body copy, headings, and FAQ disclaimers were not changed in this pass.</p>
